Detailed Description

Internal use function.

This function's parameters and processing may change in future SDKs.

This structure is used to map interface numbers to ipd ports.

Parameters:
type Interface type
first_ipd_port First IPD port number assigned to this interface.
last_ipd_port Last IPD port number assigned to this interface.
ipd_port_adj Different octeon chips require different ipd ports for the same interface port/mode configuration. This value is used to account for that difference.
